="preserve">A singer and musical artist.
A singer,composer and musical artist from iraq. Born in Al-Qadisiyah-iraq at 19 January 1994. Ali is considered one of the singers who sang the Iraqi song with their distinctive and wonderful tunes constantly in order to preserve its identity and a treasure trove of the musical culture that gives him success and advances it. He contributed to several works and composed many songs. He achived the iraqi celebrity award 2020.
